Tandem Computers Inc said theTelaction Corp unit of J.C. Penney Co Inc &lt;JCP> selected theTandem NonStop computer system for a new interactive homeshopping system scheduled to go into operation during thesummer.    Tandem said the new system will be the first consumercontrolled home shopping and information service delivered bycable television.    The Telaction service will be initially available to morethan 125,000 households in the Chicago test area, Tandem alsosaid. Reuter&#3;